  <h2>Quiz Instructions Spring 2024</h2>

  <i>Instructions and rules are subject to change, at the discretion of
  the instructor.</i>

<h4>Instructions</h4>
<ul>
  <li>
    Show supporting work!
  <li>
    Final answers with no supporting work receive no credit!
  <li>
    For <b>“DISCUSSION”</b> problems, use one or more complete sentences:
    <ul>
<li>      express the main idea
	  <li>use appropriate vocabulary</ul>
  <li>Scan and upload your finished quiz.
<!--    <i>Exception: No scanning and
      no Canvas upload for students taking the quiz at CAR.</i>-->
    <li><b>CHECK your upload</b> by logging in to
    Canvas and viewing your uploaded file. Files that are not uploaded
    correctly cannot be considered for grading.
</ul>

<h4>Rules</h4>
<ul>
  <li>
    No books, no notes, no computers, no calculator. Phones allowed for scanning only
    after finishing.
   <li>
    No earbuds, no air pods, no headphones.
   <li> No hats with brims.
</ul>

<h4>Honor Pledge</h4>
<ul>
  <li>
   Check and initial the Pledge box at the top of the quiz to make the
   following statement:
<ul>
  <li>
    "<i>I have not given or received any unauthorized help on this
    quiz. This work is my own.</i>"</ul>
</ul>
